1. Installed nvm:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Closed and reopened terminal.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16.0:
   nvm install 20.16.0
   nvm use 20.16.0

4. Installed Dart Sass using npm:
   npm install sass

5. Verified Sass installation:
   npx sass --version
